Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.70,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs32\fax0.1\c&H937A79&\bord0\frz24.69\pos(888.532,409.733)}雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.70,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs25\fax0.1\c&H9C84EB&\fsp3\bord0\b0\frz29.19\pos(714.667,424.934)}機密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要照著做就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這副眼鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟神宮寺見過你  得喬裝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,被冰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,本神居然被冰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  店開著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在  歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,選一個喜歡的位置坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,重新一看還真是個美女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,首先你要作為客人進入店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吃一碗她們的招牌麵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就從這裡開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一碗招牌拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  天升拉麵對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是中午卻沒有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們家主打無添加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  味道還不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,味道不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但卻沒有讓人有想再吃一次的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,首先要獲取她的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我是做這個的
